OL,3,GNEWSCCuts being communicated to BBC
OL,4,CNews personnel today
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe BBC is communicating with those
OL,7,Faffected by planned cuts to its News
OL,8,Fdivision.
OL,10,FThe new director-general Matt Brittin
OL,11,Fsent an e-mail about the savings plan
OL,12,Fthis morning (in full below).
OL,14,FKey points from the e-mail:
OL,16,F- News, Nations and Content will
OL,17,Fdeliver #160m in savings by year-end,
OL,18,Fwith a net reduction of around 550
OL,19,Froles ` part of the previously
OL,20,Fannounced 1,800`2,000 roles going over
OL,21,Fthree years.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,142,140,200,120,0,100
