PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1781698292
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCCuts being communicated to BBC
OL,4,CNews personnel today
OL,5,
OL,6,F- A further 700 roles are expected to
OL,7,Fclose across corporate divisions.
OL,9,F- All divisions will make significant
OL,10,Fsavings; some compulsory redundancies
OL,11,Fare likely, though they'll try to avoid
OL,12,Fthem. Voluntary redundancy windows are
OL,13,Fopening (more today).
OL,15,F- Some programmes will be closed.
OL,17,F- Commissioning spend across Content,
OL,18,FNews and Nations to be cut by c. #80m
OL,19,Fin 2027 ` 28.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,142,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14103
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1781698292
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCCuts being communicated to BBC
OL,4,CNews personnel today
OL,5,
OL,6,F- Broadcast TV channels and radio
OL,7,Fnetworks to be reviewed as audiences
OL,8,Fshift online.
OL,10,F- Senior leadership to be reduced by at
OL,11,Fleast 10%.
OL,13,FBBC News global director Jonathan Munro
OL,14,Fis due to issue a further communication
OL,15,Fat lunchtime. Various departmental
OL,16,Fcalls are due to take place this
OL,17,Fafternoon and tomorrow following that
OL,18,Fe-mail.
OL,20,FAll of News will come together tomorrow
OL,21,Ffor a call at 2pm, where the News Board
OL,22,Fwill take questions.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
